metadata.name: THE REST AREA
metadata.description:
Welcome to the rest area, 
Where is a wonderful desolate world.
Here is a perfect meeting space for all travelers,
included mechanic shops, Robot repair shop,
food truck, Motel, Space travel station, and Port.

This is a land full of a imaginary stories,
Free your soul and mind
And enjoy traveling in this wonderful land. 


Technique: cartoon - watercolor 
7500 x 1839 px / 300 dpi
